            "description": "Secretary and chairman of curatorial subcommittee within a diverse and international student exhibition committee charged with coordinating, curating, and displaying a multimedia show and corresponding workshops and events.\n\n\n\u25cfOrganized and facilitated two drawing workshops for university students, with 50+ in attendance.\n\n\u25cfElected Secretary to document approximately 36 hours of meeting minutes.\n\n\u25cfCreated and disseminated installation schedule using, Doodle, Microsoft Excel and Dropbox for 15 members.\n\n\u25cfCoordinated with fellow university representatives for the receipt and drop-off of materials.\n\n\u25cfConceptualized facets of exhibition, including supporting theme.\n\n\u25cfWrote three extended label texts and edited 10+ Dutch-English translations for grammar, tone-of-voice and content. \n\n\u25cfCollaborated with 15 other international students in the development and execution of exhibition conception and installation.\n",
